17:28

Rayon Sports ishobora kwegukana shampiyona

Gutsindwa kwa APR FC bitumye ikomeza kurushwa amanota ane na Rayon Sports ya mbere n'amanota 66 mu gihe hasigaye imikino ibiri ngo shampiyona irangire. APR FC isigaje guhura na Espoir FC na Police FC mu gihe Rayon Sports izakirwa na Kirehe FC mbere yo kwakira Marines FC.

Mwakoze cyane abo twabanye uyu munsi, tuzasubire ejo ku mukino uzahuza Kiyovu Sports na Police FC.

Icyo umukino uvuze ku makipe yombi

AS Muhanga ikeneye byibuze inota rimwe riyishyira mu mutuzo wo kuguma mu cyiciro cya mbere uyu mwaka kuko mu mibare byose bigishoboka dore ko Kirehe ya 14 ifite amanota 24 ku mwanya wa 15 munsi y'umurongo utukura.

APR FC yo irasabwa gutsinda uyu mukino kuko yamaze gusigwa amanota ane na Rayon Sports ya mbere ifite amanota 66 nyuma yo gutsinda Musanze FC ibitego 3-1 mu mukino wabaye kuri uyu wa Gatanu.

14:46

Ikaze kuri Stade ya Muhanga

Tubahaye ikaze kuri Stade Regionale y'i Muhanga hagiye kubera umukino w'umunsi wa 28 wa shampiyona hagati ya AS Muhanga na APR FC.

AS Muhanga iheruka gutsindwa na AS Kigali ibitego 2-1 mu gihe APR FC yatsinze Gicumbi FC ibitego 3-1.
